body:
Sorry for being slow to review.

@Ferruccio1984 can you give a bit more background on what was the issue with the prior method please?

My somewhat general comment is that I am not a big fan of re-implementing functionality like low-pass filters in our own way in heli.  Similarly, adding new functions like the s-shape curve in heli only.  Where possible, I think it is better to use existing functions (like the low pass filters in AP_Math) or add new functions like the s-curve to general libraries.
